socialProfiles.bio:
I studied in Utrecht. Already as a student I was involved in setting up a student travel agency and an après-ski concept. In the period of the internet bubble (1995-2000), my focus was purely on the internet and travel industry passed this period successfully. Until late 2006, I was involved in the French / Dutch company TravelHorizon. In 2007, I stepped into Zoover as a (co-) investor. In February 2009 the company has bought MeteoVista (known from weeronline.nl ). Since December 2009, both companies are located in Zeist (NL). In july 2012, the Tomorrow Focus AG (Germany) became a majorty shareholder. As the CEO I was responsible for all activities. Main focus on general business, strategy and business development. In july 2014 Tomorrow Focus AG became 100% shareholder, I will stay in the board as advisor to the board till june 2015. As industry expert at Activate Capital I am involved in reviewing & auditing of new ventures. As of the june 2015 I became CEO at one of our ventures Certimark. In September 2010 I was honoured to be named "Leading Online Entrepreneur of the Year" and received the Loey Award. I have an extensive international experience in the travel and internet industry. I speak several languages and I have a large (international) network.

 Specialismen: Hands-on manager, Specialized in Sales & Marketing ,Multilingual, Experienced in E-business, International Network
Keynote speaker & inspirator on customer centricity in a digital world. Author of When Digital becomes Human, Conversation Manager/Company.
